{"tid":2094109,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉非法集結帶署 疑遭警拍照傳群組  男童被藍絲起底 母獲禁制令","createTime":"2020-07-04T10:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T11:11:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5eb9e5b3bea2ff5271cfed90b61f842c6f8c37de","tid":2094109,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:45:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200704/TGTZXN43C5LPEQJS6U5G6R722Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200704%2FTGTZXN43C5LPEQJS6U5G6R722Q%2F&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmqS5T01Y9%2BWuDWMC0%2BQyx7Y%3D&h=eb674ddc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200704%2FTGTZXN43C5LPEQJS6U5G6R722Q%2F&h=08692358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200704/TGTZXN43C5LPEQJS6U5G6R722Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n涉非法集結帶署 疑遭警拍照傳群組 <br />\n男童被藍絲起底 母獲禁制令<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】反送中運動爆發以來，警員不時自言受起底行動威脅生命安全，向法庭申請禁制令，禁止非法發佈警員及家屬資料。惟另一邊廂，互聯網上的藍絲建制群組不時圖文並茂流傳示威者個人資料，部份相片更疑似在警署內拍攝。一名未滿16歲的男童，早前被捕後遭警方要求戴上口罩和手袖等裝束拍照；惟他未獲保釋，相片已在撐警群組流傳。男童母親上周為兒子取得臨時禁制令，禁止任何人非法發佈男童及家人的資料；法庭昨延長禁令，直至另行頒令。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：大狀質疑違私隱例 促內部徹查<br />\n<br />\n據了解，<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F1YQy93-aySKRWfxMQ--z4EVtsg=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6UJONAU447ZWF7KWEHII33VADU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF1YQy93-aySKRWfxMQ--z4EVtsg%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6UJONAU447ZWF7KWEHII33VADU.jpg&h=bff57a71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男童當日在旺角警署扣查期間，被要求戴上口罩和手袖等裝束拍照。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未獲准保釋 照片已瘋傳<br />\n<br />\n男童最終遭扣押近30小時，至5月26日凌晨始獲釋。惟上述照片早於5月25日晚已在兩個親建制fb群組流傳，其中一個群組的名字包含「支持鄧炳強」字句。有留言批評男童是「暴徒」、「曱甴」，並且要「封殺教協」等，帖文至今有多達500次轉載。<br />\n<br />\n由於貼文內有大量<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n法官李運騰即日以閉門聆訊方式頒佈臨時禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n禁令內容包括<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n教唆或授權他人從事上述行為。<br />\n<br />\n案件昨日再訊，<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n至於會否向警方查詢照片外洩一事，律師仍須索取進一步指示和法律意見。本報曾就此事向警方查詢，至截稿前未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCA1080/20"},{"pid":"2e706491d7a573e9b441ecf14ddae0a87cd4e39d","tid":2094109,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:47:02.000Z","msg":"啲姨媽姑姐先至係最仆街"},{"pid":"6905b592c4d18551449ca76810260c5599e1c0c0","tid":2094109,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"根本係警察將男童既個人資放哂比藍絲"},{"pid":"4c594c47915e6734beae5e5a402af172b925b1de","tid":2094109,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:00:11.000Z","msg":"[正視聽] 黑警流出被捕人士嚮狗屋裡面影嘅相, 係合謀嚴重妨礙司法公正<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2092244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2092244</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f3bb71a809796db5ef7a534c5765b9cd81b4a46e","tid":2094109,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:00:35.000Z","msg":"黑警妨礙司法公正冇後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1b95236410e57272f931793b3c47523cbd3567","tid":2094109,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e706491d7a573e9b441ecf14ddae0a87cd4e39d","tid":2094109,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:47:02.000Z","msg":"啲姨媽姑姐先至係最仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"D相係嚮狗屋裡面影<br />\n得d狗可以獲取及share出去"},{"pid":"cfb34ab64659de81f02dc53123d95d849fe06180","tid":2094109,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3bb71a809796db5ef7a534c5765b9cd81b4a46e","tid":2094109,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:00:35.000Z","msg":"黑警妨礙司法公正冇後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:11:34.000Z","msg":"私隱專